	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Proton Pass for Alfred

Requires Proton Pass CLI (pass-cli) on your PATH. Install:
  brew install pass-cli
  pass-cli login

Keywords:
  pp           Search your Proton Pass items
                 ⏎  copy password (clipboard auto-clears after 45s)
                 ⌘⏎ copy username/email
                 ⌥⏎ copy TOTP code
                 ⌃⏎ open first URL in browser
                 ⇧⏎ show item details (no secrets revealed)
  ppgen N      Generate a random N-character password (default 20) and copy

Workflow variables:
  PP_CACHE_TTL    Seconds before re-indexing items (default 60)
  PP_CLIP_CLEAR   Seconds before auto-clearing the clipboard (default 45; 0 = never)
</string>
